# ARC mininmal Example GC-MS metabolomics

This is a minimal Example ARC packaging a GC-MS plant metabolomics dataset with metadata

## Data origin

- Sampels originally measured as part of project "15-0001_Dominik_Brilhaus" at CMML ([CEPLAS metabolism & metabolomics lab](https://www.ceplas.eu/en/research/plant-metabolism-and-metabolomics-facility/)) HHU  
- Published under: <https://doi.org/10.1104/pp.15.01076>
- On-premise ID of this ARC: `22-0005_DominikBrilhaus_ARC`

## Setting up the arc structure using arcCommander

```bash
# initialize the structure
arc init 

# set up investigation 
arc i create --identifier samplearc_metabolomics 

# add study folders to place input material and data
arc study add -s TalinumFacultativeCAM
arc study add -s CMML_standards

# add assay folder to place assay data
arc assay add -s TalinumFacultativeCAM -a GCqTOF_targets
arc assay add -s TalinumFacultativeCAM -a MassHunter_targets
```

